  "text": "The growth of online social networks has been an important factor in shaping our lives for the 21st century. 68 % of adults in the US, also accounting for those who do not use Internet at all, are Facebook users. [CITATION_1] Over the past few years, an ecosystem of online social-network platforms has emerged, serving di erent needs and purposes: being connected with close friends, sharing news and being informed, sharing photos and videos, making professional connections, and so on.",
